items.name: Mei (Overwatch) LORA
items.description:
My sixth Overwatch LORA. Mainly focused on original appearance + a little bit of Lunar.

  • Original - back to being a bit more modular this time around - mei, brown eyes, hair bun, hair stick, glasses. Whatever you drop won't appear, so changing hairstyles and removing glasses shouldn't be a problem. For original armor - fur coat, fur-trimmed coat, fur footwear.

  • Lunar - mei, meilunar, dress, hair bun, hair stick

Checked strength range is 0.6-0.8. Strength 1 also felt stable enough, so feel free to experiment.

This time around issue were glasses - they interfered with burning in eyes quite a bit, so you gotta prompt for original brown color.

If you liked my work, you can donate here.

Review and comment with your experiences, I would appreciate whatever feedback you can provide in order to continue improving my technique.

Trained on Anything V4.5 with anime.vae.pt.

Samples are 512x768, without HighRes.fix, using OrangeCocoa 50/50 Mix , with OrangeMix VAE, and using EasyNegative embedding, CLIP Skip 2. Inpaint examples are txt2img with 1 single inpaint done on face (I will comment on exceptions).

items.name: Pramanix [Arknights] Freefit LORA
items.description:
Updated with a much better dataset.

NSFW compatible. YMMV with back shots.

Preview images use different epochs from various stages of development and are there to give you an idea of what the LORA should look like, more or less.

Some parts of her alternate costume, Caster's Frost, may appear if you try to prompt for the proper tags, but will not fully emerge. This is intentional as this LORA focuses on Pramanix's base outfit.

Pramanix is complicated and needs a lot of tags to appear right. This is a requirement for freefit LORAs, and will allow you to put her into most scenarios.

Works fine at 1 weight. Adjust lower as needed.

Paste or change up the following:

1girl, tail, large tail, animal ears, leopard ears, grey eyes, detailed eyes, white hair, multicolored hair, very long hair, wavy hair, black cape, turtleneck, white dress, hip vent, pelvic curtain, long sleeves, wide sleeves, belt, grey thighhighs, fur-trimmed boots, black boots, circlet, bead necklace

Put (circlet, tiara, head chain, necklace:1.2) into negatives if you want to obliterate Pramanix's jewelry out of existence.

items.name: Photorealistic Womb Tattoos 逼真私密纹身
items.description:
This is a (very nsfw!) LoRA for generating tattoos between the navel and vagina.

Release notes:

V5.1.15 changed trigger word "stomach" to "crotch", end results are similar to 5.0 with less training required

V5.0.25 Strongly recommended upgrade. Improved compatibility when using additional LoRAs and checkpoints. Please see the generation grids for the improvement between versions.

V4.0.1 is a leap forward in overall quality and consistency of output. Significantly reduced occurrences of common defects like tattoos on tits, multiple tattoos, fused clothing/tattoo, and more.

V3.0.1 keeps the improved photorealism from v2.0.1, now with a more unified tattoo style. The designs are clearer and better placed, and at lower LoRA weights. Recommended upgrade for any users of V2.0.1 or earlier.

V2.0.1 is a massive improvement in overall photorealism.

V1.0.1 initial release

Instructions:

All example used a weight of 0.75, but a wide range from 0.25-1 can give good results.

The best trigger word is "tattoo on stomach"

If you enjoyed this LoRA, please consider leaving a review. Your feedback helps develop better content. More Jiwenji Creations

Versioning history:

major.minor.patch

major indicates a change in at least one of training data, tagging, or LoRA generation methodology. You can use the prompt from any image with the same major version and it will operate under similar conditions.
minor indicates nothing important unless indicated in release notes

patch indicates the number of training epochs, default is 1

items.name: Sakura Chiyono O (umamusume)
items.description:
LoCon and LoRA and of Sakura Chiyono O (umamusume)

First one is LoCon ver. Second one is LoRA ver.

All of my works is free. If you'd like to support me, feel free to buy me a coffee. 👍

Notice

  1. If you use LoCon version, please install extension on WebUI.

  2. LoCon version has a twice size as lager than LoRA version.

  3. I experiment on LoCon what parameter is optimal.

  4. Preview images has all same settings, only LoCon/LoRA differ.

MAYBE NOT COMPATIBLE WITH AOM3A2, AOM3A3 model.

Maybe later, I will make chiyo with 'Sakura eye' model. maybe not. 🤔

Recommend options

  • LoRA weight 0.8~1.0

  • LoCon weight 0.6~0.7

  • Trigger words

    • base

      • sakura chiyono o \(umamusume\)

    • Racing competition clothes :

      • fingerless gloves, black gloves, collarbone, detached sleeves, wide sleeves, long sleeves, sleeveless, sailor collar, bare shoulders, japanese clothes, pink kimono, sash, obi, ribbon trim, pleated skirt, white skirt, white thighhighs, sandals

      • (optional) cherry blossom

    • Tracen school uniform :

      • white thighhighs, tracen school uniform, purple shirt, pleated skirt, puffy short sleeves, white skirt, puffy sleeves, summer uniform, frilled skirt, sailor collar, sailor shirt, miniskirt, frills

    • Casual clothes :

      • collarbone, alternate costume, pink sweater, long sleeves, white shirt, floral print, casual, pantyhose, shoulder bag, shorts, checkered skirt

    • Summer(SSR support) clothes :

      • swimsuit, navel, bare shoulders, off shoulder, official alternate costume, collarbone, pink bikini, frills, cleavage, off-shoulder bikini, frilled bikini, bridal garter, wrist scrunchie

      • (optional) holding water gun, water gun,

Use animefull based model

  • Settings

    • Stable Diffusion WebUI by Automatic1111

    • DPM++ Series(SDE Karras, 2M Karras, etc.)

    • about 20 steps, CFG scale 3.5~6.5

    • kl-f8-anime2.vae

    • CLIP skip = 1

    • Use highres. fix to get higher quality image

      • Upscaler : Latent series

      • Denoising strength 0.50~0.65

LoRA training info

  • trained on sd-scripts by kohya_ss. Thank you a lot!

  • based on Animefull-pruned

  • 115 images of Sakura Chiyono O

    • 4x low quality 48 images

    • 8x medium quality 36 images

    • 16x high quality 47 images

    • => 1 epoch = 1232 images

  • replaced character feature tags with sakura chiyono o \(umamusume\)

    • horse girl, horse tail, pink hair, blue eyes, etc.

  • resolution : 768x768

  • rank=alpha=16 (LoRA, LoCon)

  • conv_rank=conv_alpha=16 (LoCon)

  • batch size = 4

  • other training settings is included in training_data.zip

This LoRA may be compatible with animefull-based models (ex. AbyssOrangeMix Series...)

All uploaded images are generated by AOM3A1

items.name: Two heads LORA
items.description:
Two heads are better than one!

Trained on URPM 1.3, use that model for best result. But it works quite well with other models.

Recommended weight: 1.0-1.3

For best result prompt with the following structure:

<style> of 2heads, woman, <framing of picture>, <actions>, <skin color/race>, <hair>, <other details of subject>, <clothes>, <background>

Works surprisingly well on a wide variety of styles, even non photorealistic ones.

Hi-rez fix recommended.

Also if you pose the subject in the center you can use latent couple webui extension to give additional prompts to the two sides of the image so you can make each head have different expression or hair color.

For three breasts you can use tribreasts, double cleavage tags. If you don't like them put it in negative prompt as it will sometimes generate it like that without those prompts.

items.name: Göll (Record of Ragnarok / Shuumatsu no Valkyrie) Character LORA
items.description:
LORA of the Character Göll/Geru from Record of Ragnarok.

Trigger word is geru.

Alternatively, use <lora:geru:1> (Where "geru" would be the filename of the lora).

If you use the web-UI you can also select it on this button.

Unfortunately there aren't many clear pictures of her so this LORA isn't perfect. It is not that flexible, it can be hard sometimes to change outfits, expressions etc.

Lowering the weight (0.7-0.9) gives some flexibility but then it sometimes loses some character traits (hair color, eye color etc.). You can fix this by prompting those manually.

Also it sometimes generates Brunhildes body partially of screen.

That's because pretty much all of the training data was screenshots from the anime and Brunhilde is usually standing next to her.

It also really likes stone walls and pillars in the background for the same reason.

Generally you just have to experiment a bit and adjust/fix with prompts accordingly.

Trained on GrapefruitV4

Works well on most models I tested, check example images for images with specific models.

items.name: Chefskiss V1
items.description:
A merge of Protogen v2.2 and AloeVera's - SimpMaker 3k3 at 50% weight.

This model is extraordinarily versatile character generation model and is good all-around from realistic, to heavily stylized, and can be especially good at hands.

I use stable diffusion to generate reference images for my artwork, and I am very picky about artistic, and anatomically accurate references. Given a well-written prompt, this model never disappoints.

Use stabilityai's 'vae-ft-ema-560000-ema-pruned.'

Tips:

Use negative prompts: deformed fingers, big breasts, extra fingers,

Use weights: (from_behind:1.1), (realistic eyes:1.2), (athletic body:1.4),

Use artists: by kaethe butcher, greg tocchini, virgil finlay,

Study the prompts in the example images.

Use lower CFG scales: Somewhere between 7 and 10 works best, however, Simpmaker 3k3 works best with higher CFGs, in the range of 16 to even 20, so you'll really have to experiment. Higher scales have a tendency to generate multiple arms, too many fingers, strange faces & eyes, etc.

items.name: Trigun: Stampede LoRA
items.description:
Creating these models takes time, money, and effort and it's great when that effort is rewarded. If you really like it you can buy me a coffee ☕.

If you like this model please consider checking out some of my other projects. I've made LoRAs to emulate the style of Super Crooks, Fullmetal Alchemist, Death Note, Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse, Cyberpunk: Edgerunners, and Chainsaw Man.

This is Just a LORA that emulates the style of the show Trigun: Stampede. Depending on the subject you're trying to create, you'll need to play around with the strength. 0.65 strength seems to work best. All these images were created with Dreamshaper and Deliberate as the models. X-formers is on.

I trained it on around 6,000 still images from the show, so it's quite good at emulating the style. No need to give it a particularly lengthy prompt these images were generated with really simple prompts.

This LORA mixes well with others as well. So if you want a trained character/person in the Trigun: Stampede style that's possible. If you have any questions, comments, or concerns feel free to send me a message. I'm happy to chat about my methodology.

Going forward I'm going to upload the training data for all my models. Gathering these images in this quantity isn't something everyone in the community can do, so providing them will give model makers stronger tools.

items.name: Elysia 5in1 Lora
items.description:
Brief

This is a multi-identifier Lora of the lovely Elysia from Honkai impact. I have included all 4 costumes in game into one Lora, and you can easily switch between them with prompts

Lora weight suggest to set between 0.7-0.9.

Changing costume

The 5 costumes can be summoned by prompt as:

  1. Default costume: elysia \(miss pink elf\) \(honkai impact\), single glove, thigh boots, black shorts

  2. The herrscher costume: elysia \(herrscher of human:ego\) \(honkai impact\), white gloves, white boots

  3. The cute maid costume: elysia-maid, maid gloves, black high heels, maid, white thighhighs, maid headdress, apron

  4. The swimsuit: elysia-swimsuit, swimsuit, sandals, necklace

  5. The Chinese New Year costume: elysia-CNY

Some of the clothing prompts can be removed depending on your composition.

Training

10+2 epochs with high+low RL. for more details, please visit my hugging face page, I`ll post the training details and processes there: https://huggingface.co/okingjo/Multi-identifier_LORA_Model

Follow me on twitter and huggingface for more fun!

items.name: WAS Jaeger
items.description:
WAS Jaeger

A Pacific Rim Jaeger Textual Inversion Faux Style

Usage:

Ending your prompt with the following segments is probably the best method. Name may differ for different versions.

  • art by WAS-Jaeger

  • art by [(WAS-Jaeger):0.5] (Less effect)

  • art by (WAS-Jaeger) (More Effect)

  • art by [((WAS-Jaeger)):1.5] (Extreme Ultra Mode)

  • ... etc

Example Positive Prompt(s):

  • ((portrait shot)) A giant jaeger, {smokey background|burning background|dark background|back background|storming background|raining background|city skyline background|ocean background}, action pose, art by [((WAS-Jaeger)):1.5], good hand, best hand, 4k, high-res, masterpiece, best quality, ((Hasselblad photography)), sharp focus

  • (((explosion, fire, tendrils, floating orb, floating junk, energy, multiple subjects))), NG_DeepNagetive_V1_75T,(greyscale:1.2), ((nude)), paintings, sketches, (worst quality:2), (low quality:2), (normal quality:2), lowres, normal quality, ((monochrome)), ((grayscale))

Notes:

Model used is "TAM_LOFI" (my name for it) which is a mix of TheAlly's Mix III: Revolutions (for dark outputs) and LOFI model. Multiplied at 0.5 weighted sum.

❤ Hearts and 🖼️ Reviews let me know you want moarr! :3
